    Description: Takes a stream and outputs an array of Record objects.

    • Method Detail

      • getRecordClass

        public static java.lang.Class<? extends Record> getRecordClass(int sid)
        Debug / diagnosis method

        Gets the POI implementation class for a given sid. Only a subset of the BIFF records are actually interpreted by POI. A few others are known but not interpreted (see UnknownRecord.getBiffName(int)).

        (RST/ diagnosis方法获取给定sid的DOE实现类。实际上，只有BIFF记录的一部分被PRI解释。其他一些已知但未解释（请参阅UnknownRecord.getBiffName（int））。)
        Parameters:
        sid - the record sid(sid -记录sid)
        Returns:
        the POI implementation class for the specified record sid. null if the specified record is not interpreted by POI.(指定记录sid的DOE实现类。如果指定的记录未被兴趣点解释，则为空。)
